    # in order: torus radius,torus thickness radius. The parameters for a cone
    # are, in order: tan(base angle), height. The parameters for a cylinder
    # are, in order: radius, half-length.It is aligned to the z axis by
    # default.The parameters for a cylindrical tube are, in order: inside
    # radius,outside radius, half-length. It is aligned to the z axis by
    # default.The parameters for a cylindrical helix are, in order: helix
    # radius,tube radius, helix total height, pitch (height between two
    # consecutive loops).The parameters for a cut hollow sphere are, in order:
    # sphere radius,cut thickness, wall thickness. The parameters for a death
    # star are, in order: sphere radius,smaller sphere radius, distance
    # between centers.The parameters for a superquadric are, in order: a, b,
    # c, r, s, t, epsilon. The first three are half-lengths in x, y, and z.The
    # next three are the blockiness in the x, y, and z directions.The last is
